research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for Tiki Island Village, TX, include the Mayor and five Aldermen. The Mayor Pro Tem is also an Alderman. Information was gathered from the Texas Municipal League City Officials Directory, Texas State Directory Online, and the official Village of Tiki Island website. There were some discrepancies between sources regarding the full list of Aldermen, with the official Village of Tiki Island website being prioritized for the current Alderman roster.
